t berkshire hathaway website wwwclaytonhomescom clayton homes is the united states largest builder of manufactured housing and modular homes clayton homes is a component company of warren buffetts berkshire hathaway claytons corporate headquarters are in maryville tennessee its subsidiaries include vanderbilt mortgage st mortgage the nations largest manufactured home lender and insurance company homefirst agency contents  history  operations  hope for the warriors  controversy  see also  references  external links historyedit clayton homes was founded in  by jim clayton in  clayton homes established its own mortgage company and added a manufacturing division in  the company went public in  trading on the new york stock exchange each year from  through  clayton homes was named on the forbes list of the best small companies in america kevin clayton jim claytons son took over the company in  in  clayton earned a revenue of  billion it was acquired by berkshire hathaway inc in  for  billion cerberus capital management also expressed interest in bidding for the company the certificate of merger was filed in delaware and clayton stock was removed from the new york stock exchange in  clayton homes revenue was  billion clayton homes sold its landlease communities business to denverbased yes companies llc in  the deal involved  properties in  states the ihouse brand was introduced in may  as a green energy efficient home by  clayton homes had sold over  million homes in  clayton launched the ehome as a more affordable version of the ihouse in  clayton worked with oak ridge national library and architectural firm skidmore owings  merrill to produce a d printed house and car which share a single energy unit clayton homes expanded into the traditional home building market with the acquisition of georgiabased homebuilder chafin communities in  and tennesseebased goodall homes in  clayton acquired river birch homes based in maryville alabama in april  the following month clayton hosted its first birminghambased home show the show had  attendees and featured  homes from  facilities that same month clayton announced that it would partner with nonprofit next step to build a modular duplex in waco texas on a lot owned by neighborworks waco in order to create affordable housing in the greater waco area in  clayton homes was recognized as number  on forbes list of americas best employers the company introduced a line of tiny homes during fall  with the debut of its low country prototype in north carolina the designer series received media acclaim from usa today the post and courier among others on july   clayton properties group announced the purchase of home building operator birmingham alabamabased harris doyle homes with this purchase berkshire hathaways clayton unit lands its fifth sitebuild purchase showing emerging synergies among warren buffetts housing ecosystem of companies operationsedit clayton homes produces homes under the brand names of buccaneer homes cavalier homes clayton homes crest homes giles industries golden west homes karsten company marlette homes norris homes schult homes and southern energy homes clayton homes also owns retail brands oakwood homes truvalue homes and luv homes in  clayton acquired gi homes a familyrun company based in new york hope for the warriorsedit in  clayton homes released the patriot home model and partnered with the hope for the warriors veterans assistance group clayton gave a check for  to the organization in january hope for the warriors works with veterans from all branches of the military as well as post  active duty national guard and reserve service members in may  clayton presented a  check to the organization controversyedit clayton homes was involved in a lawsuit in  with fema after providing trailers as part of hurricane katrina relief which were found to contain formaldehyde afterwards one of  prefab shelters provided to haiti through the clinton foundation after the  earthquake was found to have a formaldehyde level of  ppb a very high level according to a scientist specializing in indoor pollutants at lawrence berkeley national laboratory in  a news story claimed that clayton homes unfairly targets and exploits minority home buyers clayton homes was further criticized for its alleged use of corrupt business practices the company has denied discriminating against its customers or its workers warren buffett the ceo of berkshire hathaway defended clayton against predatory lending claims in an interview saying we have  loans on the books and in the last  years ive not received one letter of complaint from anybody see alsoedit united states portal companies portal referencesedit  a b c ariel schwartz  may  clayton homes ihouse combines energy efficiency and modular affordability fast company retrieved  june    a b wendy koch december   clayton homes joins prefab green building boom with  ehome usa today retrieved june     andrew ross sorkin  july  buffett wins battle to buy clayton homes the new york times retrieved  june     clayton homes forbes retrieved  june    a b dedrick muhammad  january  call for federal investigation into report of racially discriminatory predatory lending huffington post retrieved  june    prevost lisa  financing manufactured homes the new york times issn  retrieved    chambers williams april   clayton homes buys alabama manufacturedhousing company knoxville news sentinel retrieved june     a b c jennifer reingold january   the ballad of clayton homes fast company retrieved june     a b duncan mansfield february   trailer park king makes big business after humble beginnings in tennessee kentucky new era   small company initial public offerings june  inc retrieved june     lawrence a cunningham december   ocwen would do well to follow the lessons of berkshires clayton homes the new york times retrieved june     a b berkshire hataway agrees to acquire clayton homes wall street journal april   retrieved june     andrew ross s