reate affordable housing in the greater waco area in  clayton homes was recognized as number  on forbes list of americas best employers the company introduced a line of tiny homes during fall  with the debut of its low country prototype in north carolina the designer series received media acclaim from usa today the post and courier among others on july   clayton properties group announced the purchase of home building operator birmingham alabamabased harris doyle homes with this purchase berkshire hathaways clayton unit lands its fifth sitebuild purchase showing emerging synergies among warren buffetts housing ecosystem of companies operationsedit clayton homes produces homes under the brand names of buccaneer homes cavalier homes clayton homes crest homes giles industries golden west homes karsten company marlette homes norris homes schult homes and southern energy homes clayton homes also owns retail brands oakwood homes truvalue homes and luv homes in  clayton acquired gi homes a familyrun company based in new york hope for the warriorsedit in  clayton homes released the patriot home model and partnered with the hope for the warriors veterans assistance group clayton gave a check for  to the organization in january hope for the warriors works with veterans from all branches of the military as well as post  active duty national guard and reserve service members in may  clayton presented a  check to the organization controversyedit clayton homes was involved in a lawsuit in  with fema after providing trailers as part of hurricane katrina relief which were found to contain formaldehyde afterwards one of  prefab shelters provided to haiti through the clinton foundation after the  earthquake was found to have a formaldehyde level of  ppb a very high level according to a scientist specializing in indoor pollutants at lawrence berkeley national laboratory in  a news story claimed that clayton homes unfairly targets and exploits minority home buyers clayton homes was further criticized for its alleged use of corrupt business practices the company has denied discriminating against its customers or its workers warren buffett the ceo of berkshire hathaway defended clayton against predatory lending claims in an interview saying we have  loans on the books and in the last  years ive not received one letter of complaint from anybody see alsoedit united states portal companies portal referencesedit  a b c ariel schwartz  may  clayton homes ihouse combines energy efficiency and modular affordability fast company retrieved  june    a b wendy koch december   clayton homes joins prefab green building boom with  ehome usa today retrieved june     andrew ross sorkin  july  buffett wins battle to buy clayton homes the new york times retrieved  june     clayton homes forbes retrieved  june    a b dedrick muhammad  january  call for federal investigation into report of racially discriminatory predatory lending huffington post retrieved  june    prevost lisa  financing manufactured homes the new york times issn  retrieved    chambers williams april   clayton homes buys alabama manufacturedhousing company knoxville news sentinel retrieved june     a b c jennifer reingold january   the ballad of clayton homes fast company retrieved june     a b duncan mansfield february   trailer park king makes big business after humble beginnings in tennessee kentucky new era   small company initial public offerings june  inc retrieved june     lawrence a cunningham december   ocwen would do well to follow the lessons of berkshires clayton homes the new york times retrieved june     a b berkshire hataway agrees to acquire clayton homes wall street journal april   retrieved june     andrew ross sorkin july   buffett wins battle to buy clayton homes the new york times retrieved june     belated suitor woos clayton homes usa today july   retrieved september     andrew ross sorkin july   buffett wins battle to buy clayton homes the new york times retrieved september   